# WEATHER LABS (Weather Alert Messaging System)

A messaging application that allows the user to register and receive weather forecasts, based on their location.
The users will be able to change their location and frequency of the updates.

# Instructions
 - Register/Subscribe.
 - Provide the location.
 - Receive weather forcast daily.

